@@TJvAlarms.DoAlarm
Summary
  Calls the OnAlarm event.
Description
  DoAlarm is a protected method that will call the assigned OnAlarm event if present. It's intended for
  descendants to call the OnAlarm event from their own code.
Parameters
  Alarm       - Reference to the alarm that fired.
  TriggerTime - The time the alarm went off.

